{"tid":892933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨參院改選失利　選民氣得比中指","createTime":"2018-11-07T08:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T08:37:59.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"04a52532ef9deb742eea461231461256f2cd1e44","tid":892933,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:37:59.000Z","msg":"民主黨德州參議員候選人歐魯克（Beto O'Rourke）原先被看好，可以擊敗共和黨對手克魯茲（Ted Cruz）。選前1年的民調幾乎都是歐魯克勝過克魯茲，沒想到最後卻僅以數個百分點敗北。當計票人員宣布克魯茲獲勝時，台下歐魯克的支持者忍不住比中指抗議，還有人難過落淚。<br />\n46歲的歐魯克曾是龐克搖滾樂團成員，他擔任過3屆眾議員，被視為民主黨新星。雖然此次敗選，仍有支持者看好他未來將出馬角逐更高職位。<br />\n除了歐魯克以外，原先被看好可拿下佛州州長寶座的民主黨參選人基爾林（Andrew Gillum）也敗選。喬治亞州長候選人亞伯拉姆斯（Stacey Abrams）也未能成功勝選，成為美國史上首位非裔女性州長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181107/1461884\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181107%2F1461884&d=vfGss2qHe%2BsvPngnLM%2FXEQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=af84e42f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181107%2F1461884&h=5b4e976d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181107/1461884</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181107/640_92f053e69e4ce9ab6a84b6a295f4df30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181107%2F640_92f053e69e4ce9ab6a84b6a295f4df30.jpg&h=a4091da3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 舉中指，代表條臭西今晚想俾男人屌"}]}